msgstr ""

#. Description of the plugin
msgid "Obtain GDPR (DSGVO) and ePrivacy (EU cookie law) compliant opt-in consent. Find cookies and fill all legal information in your cookie banner. More than just a cookie notice!"
msgstr ""

