#: inc/overrides/pro/view/TcfBanner.php:1
msgid "Some services set cookies and/or process personal data without following standards for communicating consent. These services are classified into several groups. So-called essential services are used on the basis of a legitimate interest and cannot be opted out (an objection may have to be made by email or letter according to the privacy policy), whereas all other services are used only after consent."
